<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Backing> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Argument> .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Backing> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Sort of credentials that certifies the warrant - e.g., the OWL 2 document specifications." .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Backing> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> "http://purl.org/spar/amo/Backing" .
# 
# https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Cause
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Cause> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Cause> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Descriptor> .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Cause> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A situation that, by means other than motivating a violational or non-violational action caused the situation presented in the artifact." .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Cause> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> "https://www.sfu.ca/rst/05bibliographies/bibs/ISI_RS_87_190.pdf" .
# 
# https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Circumstance
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Circumstance> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Circumstance> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Descriptor> .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Circumstance> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The proposition providing the situation presents the framework for interpreting the artifact." .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Circumstance> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> "https://www.sfu.ca/rst/05bibliographies/bibs/ISI_RS_87_190.pdf" .
# 
# https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Claim
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Claim> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Claim> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Argument> .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Claim> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A fact that must be established - e.g., 'This is a consistent OWL ontology'." .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Claim> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> "http://purl.org/spar/amo/Claim" .
# 
