<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Descriptor> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Descriptor> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Proposition> .
# 
# https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Elaboration
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Elaboration> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Elaboration> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Descriptor> .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Elaboration> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Additional details about the situation or some element of subject matter related to the artifact." .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Elaboration> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> "https://www.sfu.ca/rst/05bibliographies/bibs/ISI_RS_87_190.pdf" .
# 
# https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Evaluation
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Evaluation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Evaluation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Descriptor> .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Evaluation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "a proposition related the situation in the artifact to degree of context's positive regards toward the situation presented in the artifact." .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Evaluation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> "https://www.sfu.ca/rst/05bibliographies/bibs/ISI_RS_87_190.pdf" .
# 
# https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Evidence
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Evidence> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Evidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Argument> .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Evidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A fact that represents a foundation for the claim - e.g., 'This ontology was developed in OWL'." .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Evidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> "http://purl.org/spar/amo/Evidence" .
# 
