<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Idea> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Idea> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Argument> .
# 
# https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Interpretation
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Interpretation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Interpretation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Descriptor> .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Interpretation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "a proposition relates the situation presented in the artifact to a framework of ideas not involved in the artifact itself." .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Interpretation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> "https://www.sfu.ca/rst/05bibliographies/bibs/ISI_RS_87_190.pdf" .
# 
