<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Proposition> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
# 
# https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Purpose
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Purpose> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Purpose> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Descriptor> .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Purpose> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A situation to be realized through the activity in the artifact." .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Purpose> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> "https://www.sfu.ca/rst/05bibliographies/bibs/ISI_RS_87_190.pdf" .
# 
# https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Qualifier
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Qualifier> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Qualifier> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Argument> .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Qualifier> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Words or phrases that express the degree of certainty of the claim such as “certainly”, “possible”, “probably”, “presumably”, etc." .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Qualifier> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> "http://purl.org/spar/amo/Qualifier" .
