# https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Rebuttal
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Rebuttal> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Rebuttal> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Argument> .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Rebuttal> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Restrictions that may be applied to the claim - 'Unless a reasoner for OWL 2 proves that it is not consistent'." .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Rebuttal> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> "http://purl.org/spar/amo/Rebuttal" .
# 
# https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Restatement
