<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Restatement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Descriptor> .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Restatement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "a proposition restates the artifact, where the proposition and the artifact are of comparable bulk." .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#Restatement> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> "https://www.sfu.ca/rst/05bibliographies/bibs/ISI_RS_87_190.pdf" .
