# 
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#causes> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "the situation presented in the proposition as a cause for the volitional or non-violation action presented in the artifact" .
<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#causes> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> "https://www.sfu.ca/rst/05bibliographies/bibs/ISI_RS_87_190.pdf" .
# 
