<https://w3id.org/twc/sudo/ontology#elaborates> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> "The proposition presents additiona detail about the situation or some element of subject mattern which is presentes in the artifact or inferentially accessible in N in one or more of the way listed below;\nset: member\nabstract : instance \nwhole : part\nprocess : step\nobject : attribute\ngeneralization : specific" .
